どのように活用していくのか、参画大学にどのようなコ…", "…構築に向けて、大学ファンドの運用益をどのように活用していくのか、参画大学にどのようなコミットを求めるのか、そうした点についての基本的考え方を…"]}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120405261X00220210125/24", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120405261X00220210125/26", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120405261X00220210125/28", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120405261X00220210125/31", "sentence": []}]}]}, {"date": "2022-02-10", "meeting": [{"meeting_name": "衆議院 予算委員会", "remarks": [{"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120805261X01420220210/63", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120805261X01420220210/69", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120805261X01420220210/99", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120805261X01420220210/101", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120805261X01420220210/103", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120805261X01420220210/105", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120805261X01420220210/107", "sentence": ["…る場合に過去の質問の使い回しが行われたりすることについては、例えば、大学の特例試験、去年、特別に新型コロナで試験が行われた例があるわけですけ…"]}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120805261X01420220210/109", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120805261X01420220210/111", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120805261X01420220210/113", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120805261X01420220210/115", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120805261X01420220210/133", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120805261X01420220210/135", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120805261X01420220210/151", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120805261X01420220210/169", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120805261X01420220210/171", "sentence": []}, {"url": "https://kokkai.ndl.go.jp/txt/120805261X01420220210/173", "sentence": []}, {"